{
  "stem": "12674.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were going to make sure that there was nobody left to tell the story.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they were going to finish us off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But as it turned out, their calendar didn't fit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were giving themselves a little bit too much time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Good for me-- and a few others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So life went on, one day after the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the winter, it was a nightmare because we didn't have any heat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have any warm clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have water tight shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have any boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I walked with-- we didn't have plastic bags, either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have newspapers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I walked around with pieces of straw from my mattress.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somebody-- and I found some old socks, which I put over my shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I found a piece of paper someplace, from a bag or something, I would wrap it around me and, and, and rags.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would have this-- and I would have this over my feet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what I would walk in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was encrusted with mud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even if you wanted to, there was no other way because you had to walk through there to get there and back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was no pavement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was mud.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, so life went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in April-- and sometimes in March, it started, people started to come in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Instead of trains coming out, trains used to come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the people that came out of the trains-- yeah, that's right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's where the gas chambers came from.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They told us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That, that's what it must be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just put it together now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It never occurred to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The people told us horrible stories, and we said they were all crazy.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
